{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>In January of 2016, the journal <em>Extractive Industries and Society</em> accepted my masters thesis as an original research article: <a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S2214790X16300065\">Evaluating conflict surrounding mineral extraction in Ghana: Assessing the spatial interactions of large and small-scale mining</a>.</p>\n<p>The work examines the spatial interactions of small and large-scale miners in south-central Ghana. A <a href=\"https://clarklabs.org/classification-tree-analysis/\">random forest classifier</a> was used to identify small-scale mining in <a href=\"https://landsat.gsfc.nasa.gov/\">Landsat</a> imagery, and these areas were then compared to the locations of large-scale mining concessions.</p>\n<p>Below are are the abstract and figures from the paper.</p>\n<div class=\"imageBlock\">\n<div>\n<a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/95f9e/figure_1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 400px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 110.29411764705883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Figure 1\" title src=\"/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/b38fe/figure_1.png\" srcset=\"/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/73e07/figure_1.png 100w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/dd6d8/figure_1.png 200w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/b38fe/figure_1.png 400w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/e336e/figure_1.png 600w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/46e08/figure_1.png 800w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/95f9e/figure_1.png 1156w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\">\n  </span>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/95f9e/figure_2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 400px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 110.29411764705883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Figure 2\" title src=\"/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/b38fe/figure_2.png\" srcset=\"/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/73e07/figure_2.png 100w,\n/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/dd6d8/figure_2.png 200w,\n/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/b38fe/figure_2.png 400w,\n/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/e336e/figure_2.png 600w,\n/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/46e08/figure_2.png 800w,\n/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/95f9e/figure_2.png 1156w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\">\n  </span>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/95f9e/figure_1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 400px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 110.29411764705883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Figure 1\" title src=\"/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/b38fe/figure_1.png\" srcset=\"/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/73e07/figure_1.png 100w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/dd6d8/figure_1.png 200w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/b38fe/figure_1.png 400w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/e336e/figure_1.png 600w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/46e08/figure_1.png 800w,\n/static/bce0fa8c613d2e92f5acb0cf33576f8d/95f9e/figure_1.png 1156w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\">\n  </span>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/95f9e/figure_2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 400px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 110.29411764705883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Figure 2\" title src=\"/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/b38fe/figure_2.png\" srcset=\"/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/73e07/figure_2.png 100w,\n/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/dd6d8/figure_2.png 200w,\n/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/b38fe/figure_2.png 400w,\n/static/ab8ef1351297ecb4922d6c2f7f6ac01d/e336e/figure_2.png 600w,\n/static/